### Chainrails — quote testnet
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chainrails/quote
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sourceChain": "BASE_TESTNET",
  "destinationChain": "ARBITRUM_TESTNET",
  "tokenIn": "{{usdcBaseSepolia}}",
  "tokenOut": "{{usdcArbitrumSepolia}}",
  "amount": "1000000",
  "recipient": "{{wallet}}",
  "amountSymbol": "USDC"
}

